His/her favorite character in the Star Wars saga is Han Solo, especially his relationship with Chewbacca and his quick, witty remarks. He/she wants to watch the trailer for the newest Star Wars movie but does not want any spoilers.

They enjoyed Zombieland overall, despite not being a big fan of Jesse Eisenberg.
